Process Hazard Analysis (PHA).  The PHA of the refrigeration system consisted of the following:

(1)	What if/checklist study; 
(2)	Facility Inspection;
(3)	seismic assessment; and
(4)	series of safety checklists.

The PHA study generated a list of recommendations for improving safety at the facility, all of which have been verified and are in process of being completed.
